ğŸ” Built with modular architecture for AI, voice, terminal, and branding separation
ğŸ§© Supports plug-and-play tools (e.g., nmap, hydra, sqlmap, beef, etc.)
ğŸ“¦ Available as a .deb installer and Dockerized runtime (in progress)
ğŸ“¸ Comes with screenshots, GIF previews, and a full video walkthrough



